# Business Intelligence Requirements

## Purpose
Support strategic decisions with insights derived from e-waste collection operations.

## Stakeholders
- Admins  
- Environmental agencies  
- Recycling companies  

## KPIs
- **Total Items Collected**: Daily, weekly, monthly  
- **Top Collectors**: Ranked by collection volume  
- **Item Category Distribution**: Percentage per category (e.g., Computers, Phones)  
- **Collection Compliance**: Number of collections attempted on restricted days  
- **Items Recycled vs Pending**: Track efficiency of recycling operations  

---

## Reporting Frequency
- **Daily Reports**: Collection summary for Admin  
- **Weekly Reports**: Collector performance & category distribution  
- **Monthly Reports**: Audit & trend analysis  

---

## Decision Support
- Identify top-performing collectors  
- Monitor high-risk areas with delayed collections  
- Track damaged vs functional items to improve recycling efficiency  
- Dashboard mockups help visualize trends and KPIs

---

### Visual Suggestions
- KPI Cards: Total collections, top collectors, pending audits  
- Line Charts: Weekly collection trends  
- Pie Charts: Distribution of item categories  
- Heatmaps: Collector activity per city/region
